# SentinelMark Local Development Environment

Copy this file to `.env` before running `docker-compose up`.

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

## Required Environment Variables

```env
# ─── Database ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POSTGRES_USER=sentinelmark
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=sentinelmark
POSTGRES_DB=sentinelmark
DATABASE_URL=postgres://sentinelmark:sentinelmark@postgres:5432/sentinelmark

# ─── Redis ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://redis:6379

# ─── Auth ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
JWT_SECRET=change-me-in-production-use-a-long-random-string
AUTH_MODE=jwt

# ─── Observability ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT=http://jaeger:4317
RUST_LOG=info

# ─── Service Ports ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# API Gateway: http://localhost:8080
# Frontend:    http://localhost:3000
# Grafana:     http://localhost:3001 (admin / sentinelmark)
# Prometheus:  http://localhost:9090
# Jaeger:      http://localhost:16686
# Adminer:     http://localhost:8081
```
